    "Deployment of an LLM's capabilities to craft a response based on the amalgamated information from the knowledge base and the user's query Semantic search has been a topic of interest for many years, aiming to improve the precision and relevance of search results by understanding the intent and contextual meaning of terms within the search query.Traditional approaches to semantic search often relied on structured knowledge graphs, ontologies, and semantic web technologies.",
